Noelle: All my friends always say they want to be Tuna anglers. Why do they say it's so fun? #portrait:noelle
Sam: Well, I think everyone just says that because Tuna brings in the big bucks. Sushi shops, Poke restaurants, even fine dining - everyone wants a good Tuna for their dishes. #portrait:sam
Noelle: Are they hard to catch? #portrait:noelle
Sam: Oh, very. They'll fight you forever, sometimes hours, before you can reel them in. Takes a real endurance battle to pull it off.#portrait:sam
Noelle: Wow! was this one tough? #portrait:noelle
